==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gentlemens agreement
<hw>Gen"tle*men's a*gree"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>An agreement
binding only as a matter of honor; often, specif., such an agreement
among the heads of industrial or merchantile enterprises, the terms of
which could not be included and enforced in a legal contract.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gentleness</ent>⟦br⟧
